</ul>

<p><font SIZE=+1><b>16:00</b> <b>Break</b></font></p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>16:30 National Authority under the CWC</font></b></p>

<ul>
<li><font SIZE=+1>Setting up National Authority:</font></li>
</ul>

<ul>
<ul>
<li><font SIZE=+1>defining its area of responsibility,</font></li>

<li><font SIZE=+1>budget for NA&nbsp;and its programme including contribution
to OPCW</font></li>
</ul>

<li><font SIZE=+1>The role of the National Authority (what are the actions
a State Party may entrust to NA?)</font></li>
</ul>

<p><b><font SIZE=+2>THURSDAY, 13 JUNE 1996</font></b></p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+2>09:00 - 12:30 Morning Session</font></b></p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>09:00 National Authority under the CWC&nbsp;(continued)</font></b></p>

<ul>
