<li><font SIZE=+1>Communications with OPCW</font></li>
</ul>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>10:30 Break</font></b></p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1>11:00 Declaration and Inspection issuess</font></b></p>

<ul>
