<HR>

<H1><B>COLLOQUIUM ON THE LEGAL PROTECTION OF THE ENVIRONMENT BEYOND
THE LIMITS OF NATIONAL JURISDICTION</B></H1>

<H3><I>Malta, May 21 and 22, 1992</I></H3>

<P>
This Colloquium was convened jointly by the Mediterranean Academy
of Diplomatic Studies of the University of Malta and the Graduate
Institute of International Studies in Geneva. It was held at the
University of Malta. The United Nations Environment Programme
was represented by Professor David J. Attard, the holder of the
UNEP Chair of Environmental Diplomacy at the Academy and convenor
of the Colloquium, and by several participants from the Mediterranean
Action Plan, including its Co-ordinator, Professor Salvino Busuttil.
The conclusions of the Colloquium were presented to the United
Nations Conference on Environment and Development in Rio de Janeiro
in June 1992 by the delegation of Malta.<HR>

