<body background="http:/images/yellow_rock.gif">
<center><h1>DCRS Personnel</h1></center>

<P>
DCRS is headed by research professor Sren Nrvang Madsen
and professor (docent) Erik Lintz Christensen.
<p>
<h2>The key personnel at the centre are:</h2>
<p>
Analog electronics, radiometers: Niels Skou, Dr. sc.<br>
Digital electronics, RTP-systems: E. Lintz Christensen, Professor (acting)<br>
SAR sensor maintenance:	E. Lintz Christensen, Professor (acting)<br>
Data processing: Jrgen Dall, Senior research ass.<br>
Science and electromagnetic modelling: Henning Skriver, Senior research ass. &
Leif T. Pedersen, Senior research ass.<br>
Systems integration: Kim Woelders, Senior research ass.<br>
Administration and flight operations: Ralf Skovgaard, Center administrator<br>
<p>
<p>
