 <HEAD><TITLE>Bjrn Bavnehj Thomsen at EMI</TITLE></HEAD>

 <BODY>

  <H1><IMG SRC="/images/bbt.jpg"> Bjrn Bavnehj Thomsen</H1>

  <STRONG>M.Sc.E.E. , Ph.D. Student</STRONG>
  <P>
  Electromagnetics Institute<br>
  DTU, Building 349, room 230<br>
  DK-2800 Lyngby<br>

  <P>Telephone: +45 45 88 14 44, ext. 3793<BR>
  Direct Dial: +45 45 25 3793<BR>
  Telefax: +45 45 93 16 34<BR>
  E-mail: <A HREF="mailto:bbt@emi.dtu.dk">bbt@emi.dtu.dk</A></P>

  <HR>

  <H2>Research</H2>

  North East Water Polynya<br>
