<H1>Welcome to Danish Center for Remote Sensing (DCRS)</H1>
headed by <a href="/DCRS/staff/snm.html">Sren Nrvang Madsen</a>, <a href="mailto:snm@emi.dtu.dk">snm@emi.dtu.dk</a><BR>
</CENTER>
