DK 2800 Lyngby<BR>
Denmark<BR>
<BR>
Telephone: +45 45 88 14 44<BR>
Telefax: +45 45 93 16 34<BR>

<P>
<H3>About DCRS</H3>
<P>
The Danish Center for Remote Sensing (<a href="DCRS/centre.html">DCRS</a>) is one of the centres
of the Danish National Research Foundation (Danmarks Grundforskningsfond).
It is located at the Dept. of Electromagnetic Systems (<a href="http://www.emi.dtu.dk/">EMI</a>), the Technical
University of Denmark (<a href="http://www.dtu.dk/">DTU</a>). The centre conducts research relating to
instruments for remote sensing and their application to Earth
observation and Earth Science. The centre is established with
a 50 million DKK grant for the period February 1, 1994 to January
31, 1999.
<P>
<HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=CENTER>
<P>
