 <HEAD><TITLE>Leif Toudal Pedersen at EMI</TITLE></HEAD>

 <BODY>

  <H1><IMG SRC="/images/ltp.gif"> Leif Toudal Pedersen</H1>

  <STRONG>Ph.D,  Research Assistent  </STRONG>
  <P>
  Electromagnetics Institute<br>
  DTU, Building 349, room _ROOM<br>
  DK-2800 Lyngby<br>

