       <dd>Binary versions of the EMI Image Display System for <a href="ftp://ms/pub/emimage/hp">HP 700</a> and <a href="ftp://ms/pub/emimage/rs6000">IBM RISC 6000</a> .
	    <p>
  <dt> EMI Image Header and I/O System version 3.</b> (Toolkit - beta)
       <dd> Image header definition and programming toolkit for interfacing
	    image files.
	    <ul>
