<B><FONT SIZE=4>newsletter</FONT><FONT SIZE=2>     </FONT><FONT SIZE=7>DCRS
<BR>
</FONT></B>
<P>
<B><FONT SIZE=4>Danish Center for Remote Sensing<BR>
