<P>
<H1>Ice in the Odden area in January and February 1993</H1>
<P><STRONG><a href="/DCRS/staff/tff.html">Tim Flintholm Fink</a> & <a href="/DCRS/staff/ltp.html">Leif Toudal Pedersen</a></STRONG><P>
<P><STRONG><a href="http://ms/dcrswww.html">Danish Center for Remote Sensing</a><BR><a href="http://www.emi.dtu.dk/">Electromagnetics Institute</a><BR><a href="http://www.dtu.dk/">Technical University of Denmark</a><BR>July 1995</STRONG><P>
You can also <a href="ftp://ms/pub/oddenice/odden-ice-report.ps">download</a> a 2.8 Mb postscript version of the report (without the image appendices).
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html18 HREF="node1.html#SECTION00100000000000000000">Contents</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html19 HREF="node2.html#SECTION00200000000000000000"> Introduction</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html20 HREF="node3.html#SECTION00300000000000000000"> Theory for sea ice and sea water</A>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html21 HREF="node4.html#SECTION00310000000000000000"> Development of new ice</A>
