</UL> 
</UL> 
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html32 HREF="node15.html#SECTION00340000000000000000"> Weather measurements at Jan Mayen</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html33 HREF="node16.html#SECTION00350000000000000000"> Ice covered area from SSM/I</A>
