  Born 26 September 1970 in Copenhagen, Denmark.<br>
  Student at Technical University of Denmark (DTU) from September 1989 until March 1995.<br>
  Student at University of Strathclyde in Glasgow, Scotland from January to June 1994.<br>
  M.Sc in Electrical Engineering 31 March 1995 from DTU. The master thesis was on microwave remote sensing of sea ice.<br>
  Worked as research assistent since 1 April 1995 at the Electromagnetics Institute, DTU.
