 <BR> <HR><A NAME=tex2html159 HREF="node3.html"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="next" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/next_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME=tex2html157 HREF="odden-ice-report.html"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="up" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/up_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME=tex2html151 HREF="node1.html"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="previous" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/previous_motif.gif"></A> <A NAME=tex2html161 HREF="node1.html"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="contents" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/contents_motif.gif"></A>  <BR>
<B> Next:</B> <A NAME=tex2html160 HREF="node3.html"> Theory for sea </A>
