<H1><A NAME=SECTION00200000000000000000> Introduction</A></H1>
<P>
In this report ice conditions in the Odden area of the Greenland Sea is addressed.
The report contains a short description of ice developments and oceanographic effects
in the area, and an extensive treatment of ERS-1 SAR images.
In figure <A HREF="node2.html#figoverall"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A> is the Odden area shown together with the east coast of 
Greenland and the island Jan Mayen.
<P>
