<BR> <HR> <P>
<H3><A NAME=SECTION00332300000000000000> Nilas</A></H3>
<P>
Nilas is a subsequent evolvement of grease ice.
It appears dark in SAR images, and it has little or no texture of significance. 
When the wind speed is low, it can be difficult to separate areas with open water
and nilas.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
