<BR> <HR> <P>
<H3><A NAME=SECTION00332400000000000000> New ice</A></H3>
<P>
All the early stages of ice formation appears dark in SAR images.
In the following the term <em>new ice</em> will be used to address new ice with an unspecified 
type.
New ice will normally consist of either grease ice or nilas.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
