<H1><A NAME=SECTION00350000000000000000> Ice covered area from SSM/I</A></H1>
<P>
The total ice covered area in the Odden region has been calculated from the SSM/I
data.<BR>
The individual images and an mpeg encoded sequence are shown in appendix <A HREF="node59.html#SECTION00700000000000000000"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A>.<BR>
The results of the ice covered area are shown in figure <A HREF="node16.html#figjan_ice"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A> and <A HREF="node16.html#figfeb_ice"><IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM ALT="gif" SRC="/u/emilib/lib/perl/latex2html/icons/cross_ref_motif.gif"></A>.
