<H1><A NAME=SECTION00400000000000000000> Ice in the Odden area in January and February 1993</A></H1>
<P>
In this chapter daily SSM/I radiometer data will be used with almost daily ERS-1 SAR
images to characterize the ice conditions in the Odden area for a period of January
and February 1993.
The single days will be addressed separately below.
<P>
<BR> <HR>
<UL> 
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html348 HREF="node18.html#SECTION00400100000000000000"> January 2 1993</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html349 HREF="node19.html#SECTION00400200000000000000"> January 8 1993</A>
<LI> <A NAME=tex2html350 HREF="node20.html#SECTION00400300000000000000"> January 11 1993</A>
