<H3><A NAME=SECTION004001900000000000000> February 8 1993</A></H3>
<P>
In the upper frame of the SAR image, a big dark area of new formed ice is present.
The rest of this frame contains open water.<BR>The lower frame has a rough appearance, with a grey background and with some dark 
features.
The background is probably mixtures of open water and pancake ice, while the dark
features are new ice.
