<H3><A NAME=SECTION004002200000000000000> February 10 1993 (2)</A></H3>
<P>
The lower 3 frames in the SAR image shows open water in the lower right corner.
Next to this open water is a dark area, which is expected to be dominated by new
ice.
The rest of the image is the same as in part (1) from February 10.
