<H3><A NAME=SECTION004003400000000000000> February 20 1993 (2)</A></H3>
<P>
In the SAR frames to the west, bright open water seen in the upper part and in
most of the left hand side.
In the lower left corner are some small dark bands of new formed ice.
The background in all the ice covered parts are grey, and it is expected to consist
of a dense pancake ice cover.
