<H3><A NAME=SECTION004003600000000000000> February 22 1993</A></H3>
<P>
In most parts of the SAR image bright open water is dominating.
Only in the central right hand side is a significant ice covered area present.
The ice is quite dark, and it is expected to be a dense concentration of pancake ice.
Between the ice are greater open water areas present.
<P>
