<B> Next:</B> <A NAME=tex2html792 HREF="node55.html"> February 24 1993</A>
<B>Up:</B> <A NAME=tex2html790 HREF="node17.html"> Ice in the </A>
<B> Previous:</B> <A NAME=tex2html784 HREF="node53.html"> February 22 1993</A>
<BR> <HR> <P>
<H3><A NAME=SECTION004003700000000000000> February 23 1993</A></H3>
<P>
In the SAR image is open water clearly present in the upper part.
The rest contains a dark background with bright open water areas in 
the foreground.
The temperature is above zero at Jan Mayen, and the ice can have a wet surface.
The background is therefore assumed to contain a high concentration of melting 
pancake ice.
<P>
<BR><HR><a HREF="sar-images/930223.jpg"><tt>SAR.930223.jpg</tt></a><BR>
<BR><a HREF="ssmi-images/930223.gif"><tt>SSMI.930223.gif</tt></a><BR>
<BR> <HR>
