<BR> <HR> <P>
<H3><A NAME=SECTION004003800000000000000> February 24 1993</A></H3>
<P>
The SAR image shows only a few bands of pancake ice within the open water.
Even though the temperature on February 24 is very low, the SSM/I image shows,
that the ice is melting away.
<P>
<BR><HR><a HREF="sar-images/930224.jpg"><tt>SAR.930224.jpg</tt></a><BR>
<BR><a HREF="ssmi-images/930224.gif"><tt>SSMI.930224.gif</tt></a><BR>
