<BR> <HR> <P>
<H3><A NAME=SECTION004003900000000000000> February 26 1993</A></H3>
<P>
The SSM/I image shows, that ice is only present in the upper left corner,
while the rest contains open water.
Some dark patterns are seen in the open water areas, and this is expected to be 
bands of pancake ice.
<P>
<BR><HR><a HREF="sar-images/930226.jpg"><tt>SAR.930226.jpg</tt></a><BR>
