<H1><A NAME=SECTION00800000000000000000> Weather measurements at Jan Mayen in January and February 1993</A></H1>
<P>
<A NAME=appweather_data>&#160;</A>
In this section the the temperature measurements from Jan Mayen is presented.
The data are delivered by <A HREF="node61.html#NMI">[NMI, 1993]</A>.
