<BR><STRONG>Table:</STRONG> Parameters needed for the pseudocylindrical projections. Types: <b>I</b>nverse, <b>S</b>pherical, <b>E</b>lliptical, and Equal <b>A</b>rea<BR>
<P>
<P>
<H2><A NAME=SECTION00404000000000000000> Conic Projections</A></H2>
<P>
