<BR><STRONG>Table:</STRONG> Parameters needed for the conic projections. Types: <b>C</b>onformal, <b>I</b>nverse, <b>S</b>pherical, <b>E</b>lliptical, and Equal <b>A</b>rea. <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="_24619_tex2html_wrap1726.gif"> <tt>south</tt> is set with <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="_24619_tex2html_wrap1728.gif">. Should be <IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="_24619_tex2html_wrap1730.gif"> otherwise<BR>
