<H1>Join NIRS' E-Mail Alert List</H1>

<P>If you're concerned about nuclear power, radioactive waste, radiation,
and sustainable energy issues...in other words, if you're a citizen of
this planet, please join NIRS' e-mail Alert list. You will receive periodic
messages (usually 5-10/month), outlining current nuclear issues and what
YOU can do to achieve change. There is no charge for this service.</P>

<P>You may either <A HREF="../../forms/e_mail_alert.html">use the form
here</A>, or e-mail your name, address, organization, phone, fax and e-mail
address to NIRS at <A HREF="mailto:nirsnet@igc.apc.org">nirsnet@igc.apc.org</A>
Or call NIRS at 202-328-0002 if you have questions or would like further
information.</P>

<P>
