<H3>Link to the international environmental/safe energy movement
</H3>
<P><BR></P>
<P>International <A HREF="http://www.t0.or.at/~C+10">No More Chernobyls web
site</A>. Information on the worldwide campaign around the Chernobyl 10th
anniversary, April 1996.</P>
<P><A HREF="http://antenna.nl/~wise">WISE</A> World Information Service on
Energy. Site includes regularly updated news from around the world and a growing
section on uranium--mining, processing, etc.  
</P>
