Slovokia.</A> Dedicated individuals fighting the Mochovce nuclear complex  and a
very repressive government. Give them a hand here. Note: Slovokian phone lines
don't always work; if you don't get through the first time, try again.</P>
<P><A HREF="http://www.grida.no/ngo/bellona/ehome/index.htm">Bellona</A>.
Information on Norwegian safe energy issues, and radiation contamination in
Russia. Bellona has risked a lot (including arrests) to get this info.</P>
<P><A HREF="http://miya.ecn.fpu.ac.jp/monju-a2e.htm">Stop Monju Breeder
Campaign</A>. The Monju Breeder reactor recently suffered a severe accident that
will probably keep it shut down for some time. Join this group in an effort to
keep it closed for good. They already have collected more than 1,000,000
signatures on Monju shutdown petitions--you can add your name at this site.</P>
<P><A HREF="http://www.deev.com/ccnr">Canadian Coalition for Nuclear
Responsibility</A>. Lots of info on plutonium, radioactive waste issues and
CANDU reactors.</P>
