<H4><B>January 14, 1997: <FONT SIZE="+1"><A HREF="russlttr.txt">171
organizations worldwide sign letter</A> to President Clinton urging him to
reject MOX fuel option approved by DOE Secretary Hazel O'Leary today</FONT>.
<A HREF="moxprint.htm">Press release for MOX letter,</A> 1/14/97.</B></H4>
<P>Note: over the next two-three weeks, NIRS will be upgrading our web server
hardware. The NIRS website will be down occasionally, though briefly, as we
prepare for the upgrade. The site will be down for about a day at the end of
this period--we will try to provide advance notice here of that date. The new
server should be much faster (especially on the NIRS webboard) and should be
worth the downtime.</P>
