in Ohio</A>, January 1997</LI>

<LI>The <A HREF="Wvstory.txt">Ward Valley story</A>, from Save Ward Valley,
January 1997</LI>

<LI>Info on <A HREF="Grndisk.txt">Green Disk Guide to a Sustainable Future</A>,
January 1997</LI>

<LI>Free the Planet <A HREF="Ftpjobs.txt">jobs and internship information</A>,
December 11, 1996</LI>

<LI>Government Accountability Project Alert: <A HREF="Gaprop.txt">Comment
now to protect DOE whistleblowers</A>. 12/96</LI>

<LI>California Ratepayers Alert: <A HREF="Carenew.txt">Protect Renewable
Energy!</A> December 1996</LI>
</UL>

<P>Newsletters available here include A Clear View, Ozone Action, New England
Environmental Network Pulse, and others. Your newsletters can be included!
Send (in ASCII or htm format) to nirsnet@igc.apc.org</P>

