<P><IMG SRC="nirsweb.gif" HEIGHT=60 WIDTH=300> </P>

<H1>International Grassroots</H1>

<P>This area consists of items produced by grassroots environmental groups
from across the globe, including newsletters, press releases, reports and
more. In short, it is anything YOU want to send us. For the most part,
these are text files. Some U.S. government reports and papers relating
to international issues are included here as well.</P>

<P>For a perspective on U.S. activities, check out our <A HREF="/grassroots/grasbbs.htm">Dispatches
from the Grassroots</A> file area.</P>

<P>This file area is indexed and you may search by keywords. There are
many more files here than those listed below. <A HREF="internationalindex.htm">Click
here to access the</A><A HREF="international index.htm"> index.</A> Note
that there are several different indexes, the one for this area is titled
&quot;international.&quot;</P>

