<H1>Alternatives to nuclear power</H1>
<HR>
<P>This file area includes documents relating to alternatives to nuclear power:
solar, wind, geothermal, etc. It also includes information on U.S. federal
budget issues relating to renewable resources. This is a new area (as of 6/4/96)
and does not yet contain a lot of information. We're hoping it will grow
quickly, and your submissions are welcome.</P> 
