<h1>NRC Weekly Information Report</h1>

<p>These are copies of the NRC Commissioner's Weekly Information Report--a
publication prepared for the Commissioners to keep them up-to-date on a
wide variety of nuclear-related issues. Upcoming safety problems, new areas
of controversy--they often show up first here. This is a prime resource
for anyone interested in nuclear power and the workings of the Nuclear
Regulatory Commission. Note: all files are in .txt format, and are not
formatted for html.</p>

<p><a href="wirindex.htm">Click here</a> to search this file area.</p>

