<h1>Daily Event Reports</h1>

<p>
<hr></p>

<p>Daily Event Reports are, just as the name implies, daily summaries of
significant events at the nation's nuclear licensees, including reactors,
fuel cycle sites, waste dumps, industrial users of radioactive materials,
etc. We began including these on NIRSNET on the Web in late May 1996. They
are fully indexed. You may search by date, by utility, by reactor, by topic
(i.e. steam generator) or just about any other way.</p>

<p><a href="derindex.htm">Click here to use the index.</a></p>

<p><a href="file:///C|/WebSite/dailyrpt/nirsbbs.htm"><img src="nirslog2.gif" border=2 height=0 width=0 align=bottom></a></p>

