<H1>Wind Energy Weekly</H1>
<HR>
<P>Wind Energy Weekly is the newsletter of the American Wind Energy
Association. This trade organization represents one of the most promising
renewable energy sources in the world--wind power. Here you can learn the latest
about wind technology, what states are doing (and not doing) to promote wind
energy, and news about federal funding for wind resources.</P> 
<P>Rather than list each issue, we have indexed them. To find a specific issue,
simply search for the date or issue number. Otherwise search for topics,
companies, etc.
<A HREF="wewindex.htm">Click here to use the index.</A></P>      
