<h1>Local Contacts for Chernobyl + 10 Activities</h1>

<p>Following are names, addresses, phone numbers and, where available,
e-mail addresses for local groups planning to participate in Chernobyl
10th commemoration activities. Groups are arranged by state, and where
appropriate, by country. If you are interested in helping with activities
in your area, please contact the local group directly. If your area is
not represented, and/or if you wish to initiate activities with your group
or in your area (and it is certainly feasible to have more than one group,
church, school, etc. participating in the same region, or even city or
town), please contact NIRS at<a href="mailto:nirsnet@igc.apc.org"> nirsnet@igc.apc.org
</a>or call 202-328-0002. Note, this list will change and will be added
to frequently over the next two months. Check here often! Thanks!</p>

<p><b><font SIZE=+1></font></b></p>

