<BODY><H1>Radioactive waste transportation routes by state</H1>
<P>These are likely radioactive waste transportation routes by state. Each
state includes a map (gif file) and a text explanation of exactly what
radioactive waste would be transported across the state if the nuclear power
industry has its way. These maps and text explanations were researched and
produced by the State of Nevada. Note, light lines on the maps indicate rail
routes, dark lines are highway routes.</P>
