<P>Transportation of commercial high-level radioactive waste is not anticipated
through Alaska, Delaware, Hawaii,  Montana, North Dakota, Rhode Island, or South
Dakota. Transportation is anticipated through the District of Columbia, but no
map is available. The rail transport route is less than one mile from the U.S.
Capitol Building. </P>
